Package: robSynth
Type: Package
Title: Robust Synthetic Data Generation
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R: person("Matthias", "Templ",
    email = "matthias.templ@fhnw.ch",
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8638-5276"))
Author: Matthias Templ [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Matthias Templ <matthias.templ@fhnw.ch>
Description: Robust synthetic data generation methods that protect data
    quality from contaminated training data.  Replaces the conditional
    models in sequential synthesis with MM-estimators (continuous) and
    weighted logistic regression (categorical), achieving bounded
    influence and high breakdown point.  Includes utility metrics
    (pMSE, KS, regression preservation, correlation) and disclosure
    risk assessment (k-anonymity, membership inference, TCAP).
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: robustbase, nnet, rpart, stats, MASS
Suggests: partykit, synthpop, ggplot2, gridExtra, riskutility, ranger,
    xgboost, tinytest, knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
